event.name: Event Dungeons
event.desc:
React with ${guild.emojis.find(emoji => emoji.name == 'pcave')} and join voice to participate.
React with ${guild.emojis.find(emoji => emoji.name == 'thicckey')} if you have any event keys and are willing to pop.
React with a class or ability if you plan to bring it to the run.

shatts.desc:
